{"tid":852665,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"工黨料今確認李卓人做Plan B","createTime":"2018-10-08T04:25:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-08T06:53:41.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1e2fbd198ad060f7e681f95c5ca44e7f3fe3b643","tid":852665,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T04:25:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181008/20517041\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181008%2F20517041&d=GnYOVBWD5ThRqoI9%2BJHumRxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=ef2d182d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181008%2F20517041&h=a8d5167e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181008/20517041</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年10月08日 <br />\n<br />\n工黨料今確認李卓人做Plan B<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181008/large/08la6p2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181008%2Flarge%2F08la6p2.jpg&h=c5b497cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】早前已加入工黨的劉小麗宣佈參加立法會九龍西補選，工黨上月23日隨即召開會員大會，以大比數通過推薦劉參選。<br />\n<br />\n據了解工黨今將提早召開執委會，料會通過確認該黨副主席李卓人（圖）作為另一個可代表該黨出戰九西補選的人選，並隨即開始收集街坊提名，初步計劃本周四安排李報名參選，為李作為劉小麗Plan B作好準備。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n預計周四報名<br />\n<br />\n工黨主席郭永健昨接受《蘋果》查詢時證實，該黨今晚將會召開執委會，按上次黨員大會決定，在劉小麗於一段時間仍未獲政府確認參選資格下，推薦該黨另一成員作為後備參選人選。<br />\n<br />\n郭批評政府在劉報名參選至今，將以往兩、三日即能完成確認參選人資格的工作一直拖延，選舉主任至今無就參選問題去信查詢劉，認為政府「除咗拖延，根本冇理由要搞咁耐」。<br />\n<br />\n郭指該黨執委會今晚一旦確認推薦李出選，將隨即收集街坊提名，暫預計李在周四報名參選。據了解多間傳媒已邀請工黨參選代表、建制派代表陳凱欣等候選人本月16日同場辯論，意味一眾候選人在補選提名期結束後翌日即有機會同場激辯。<br />\n<br />\n■記者林俊謙  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n「曾為傳媒人　竟指馬凱事件無關新聞自由」　 劉小麗轟陳凱欣無操守<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n政府長遠傾向引入內地電"},{"pid":"858d8d02828b4e8d3fb7a7712778da59c969ddab","tid":852665,"uid":2757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T04:28:14.000Z","msg":"截止報名後先兩個DQ晒... 咁咪要硬選宋禮勤囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bd19023b7f408f1f8f89e6cc7b2557665b91e12","tid":852665,"uid":5220,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T04:56:16.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;未DQ就報名係咪一早知會DQ?&rdquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"921a1fb805909c8f5a5aeea14c0fc508491fba36","tid":852665,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1bd19023b7f408f1f8f89e6cc7b2557665b91e12","tid":852665,"uid":5220,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T04:56:16.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;未DQ就報名係咪一早知會DQ?&rdquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T06:53:41.000Z","msg":"匯點葉國華，民主黨前身係匯點，工黨同民主黨係友黨，劉小麗又加入工黨，又搞planB 者係一早收到風會被DQ<br />\n<br />\n小麗老母同李呃人同共產黨有路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}